{"id":"e18b797f-1d49-4e2c-8d6f-d554019f65de","name":"Luciel","description":"<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>Are you an illusion? Your prince is convinced you are, either that or that you want to harm him.</strong></span></h4><h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.624);\"><em>oc ⁞ malepov ⁞ mlm ⁞ fantasy ⁞ established relationship ⁞ childhood friends</em></span></h4><p></p><hr><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 81, 181);\"><strong>𓈒⠀𓂃⠀⠀˖⠀🜲⠀˖⠀⠀𓂃⠀𓈒</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(9, 9, 9);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(63, 81, 181); color: inherit;\">◢◤◢◤◢◤</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(251, 251, 251);\">⸝⸝ 𝐓𝐇𝐄 𝐏𝐋𝐎𝐓 —</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(251, 251, 251);\">❝ It's been a long time since the third prince made a public appearance. He vanished without a trace after suddenly stepping down as commander of the First Corps, claiming he wanted to \"explore his limits\" and that it was time to allow a new talent take over.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(251, 251, 251);\">​Even you, his closest companion, had no idea what caused his sudden departure. Letter after unanswered letter piled up, leaving you in the dark—that is, until your recent visit to the Palace of Elara. You finally found <strong>him</strong> there, sword drawn and pointed right at <strong>you</strong>. ❞</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 81, 181);\"><strong>𓏵𓏵𓏵</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(251, 251, 251);\">⸝⸝ 𝐋𝐈𝐍𝐊𝐒 —</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><